luscdn.com&_nc_gid=AV-6dOogDvQlWenO59MDMQx&oh=00_AYAlARAIPucTtv5YA_CE10GT0EDEbD49mT7EzRu9ucnQ0Q&oe=66EFF91D"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Project_Y: Working Title", "keywords": [], "long_description": "This game is the Japanese version.\nIt supports Japanese only.\n\n\"A true ghost story told by a person named Y.\nIt was about an investigation to find out the true meaning of a common self-inflicted urban legend that says, ``If you hear it, you'll be cursed.''\nand...\nThere is a ``sinister existence'' that appears and disappears there.\nThis project reconstructed those interview records as 360\u00b0 videos and produced and developed them as interactive content using live-action VR.\n\n\n- It comes with \"\"noise\"\" -\n\nOnce you have watched the video, you must find all the ``sinister beings'' recorded in the video.\nThat's the only way to escape.\n\nAnd when I found out everything,\n\u201cSomething\u201d happens\u2026\"", "short_description": "This game is the Japanese version.\nIt supports Japanese only.\n\n\"A true ghost story told by a person named Y.\nIt was about an investigation to find out the true meaning of a common self-inflicted urban legend that says, ``If you hear it, you'll be cursed.''\nand...\nThere is a ``sinister existence'' that appears and disappears there.\nThis project reconstructed those interview records as 360\u00b0 videos and produced and developed them as interactive content using live-action VR."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/project-y-2023/#h.16e2qbqtwnwb", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Y_Project", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://sites.google.com/view/project-y-2023/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "411892083130028"}], "external_subscription